ttsdata.text: The Awesome Guy! You are grounded grounded grounded grounded grounded for life! Go to your room right now!
Yes! I grounded The Awesome Guy! Yes! I grounded The Awesome Guy! Yes! I grounded The Awesome Guy!
Look Tommy! Carla just ground me for no reason!
Carla! How dare you ground The Awesome Guy! That's it! I am calling Narcisa about this!
Oh crap! I gotta go now!
Carla! How freaking dare you ground The Awesome Guy! That's it! You are grounded for 52,985,109 years! Go to bed now!
Wa wa wa wa wa wa wa wa wa wa wa wa wa!
